<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mocktail Menu | CafeButter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f1e5;
            color: #5c3d2e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #5c3d2e;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #8b5e3b;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #5c3d2e;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5c3d2e;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #8b5e3b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Mocktail Menu | CafeButter
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Refreshing Mocktails</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Virgin Mojito <span class="price">₹150</span></h3>
            <p>Muddled mint leaves, lime juice, sugar, and soda water for a refreshing and fizzy taste.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Nojito <span class="price">₹140</span></h3>
            <p>Lime, mint, sugar, and club soda make this a crisp and light drink.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Shirley Temple <span class="price">₹160</span></h3>
            <p>Sweet and fizzy, made with ginger ale, grenadine, and a cherry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Virgin Piña Colada <span class="price">₹170</span></h3>
            <p>Pineapple juice, coconut milk, and ice blended for a tropical treat.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Citrus Fizz <span class="price">₹145</span></h3>
            <p>A tangy blend of orange, lemon, and lime juice with soda water.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Berry Lemonade Spritz <span class="price">₹155</span></h3>
            <p>Fresh berries, lemon juice, syrup, and soda for a fruity refreshment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sunset Cooler <span class="price">₹160</span></h3>
            <p>Layers of orange juice, grenadine, and soda for a sunset effect.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Apple Ginger Sparkler <span class="price">₹150</span></h3>
            <p>Bubbly and crisp with apple juice, ginger ale, and lime.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Cucumber Mint Cooler <span class="price">₹140</span></h3>
            <p>Cool and hydrating with cucumber, mint, lime, and sparkling water.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Tropical Fruit Punch <span class="price">₹175</span></h3>
            <p>A mix of pineapple, mango, and orange juice with grenadine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Watermelon Lemonade <span class="price">₹150</span></h3>
            <p>Fresh watermelon puree, lemon juice, and soda water for a fizzy touch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Ginger Lime Fizz <span class="price">₹135</span></h3>
            <p>Lime juice, ginger syrup, and sparkling water for a zesty kick.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Citrus Cooler <span class="price">₹145</span></h3>
            <p>Fresh lime, orange juice, and soda with a minty finish.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Peach Iced Tea <span class="price">₹165</span></h3>
            <p>Black tea with peach syrup, fresh peaches, and a squeeze of lemon.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Coconut Water Mojito <span class="price">₹170</span></h3>
            <p>Coconut water, lime juice, fresh mint, and a touch of honey.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
